OL,6,FPlease be advised that you may find
OL,7,Fsome of the details in Sara O'Kane's
OL,8,Freport upsetting
OL,10,FA man has told the Omagh Bombing
OL,11,FInquiry how he found his wife lying
OL,12,Fface down in rubble in the aftermath
OL,13,Fof the massacre.
OL,15,FKevin Skelton told the hearing that he
OL,16,Fcould never forget the smell of
OL,17,Fburning flesh and the cries of victims
OL,18,Fafter a Real IRA bomb devastated the
OL,19,Fcentre of the Co Tyrone town in 1998.
