OL,3,C'Some things I witnessed, no human
OL,4,Cshould have to live with'
OL,6,FMother-of-four Philomena Skelton was
OL,7,F39 when she died in the attack while
OL,8,Fon a shopping trip with her husband
OL,9,Fand three daughters.
OL,11,FMr Skelton told the inquiry that he
OL,12,Fand his wife were like "chalk and
OL,13,Fcheese".
OL,15,FHe refereed GAA games while his wife
OL,16,Fliked to stay at home knitting and
OL,17,Freading.
