OL,3,C'Some things I witnessed, no human
OL,4,Cshould have to live with'
OL,6,FHe told the inquiry that he had
OL,7,Fbrought his wife Philomena and their
OL,8,Fthree daughters into Omagh to shop for
OL,9,Fitems for school on the Saturday the
OL,10,Fbomb exploded.
OL,12,FMr Skelton said they were inside a
OL,13,Fshop when they were alerted to a bomb
OL,14,Fscare by a traffic warden.
OL,16,FHe said: "One of my daughters said as
OL,17,Fwe crossed into SD Kells, 'I wonder is
OL,18,Fthe bomb in that car?'
OL,20,F"But nobody thought, I never thought
OL,21,Fthere was a bomb.
OL,26,@xD@JOU|D@AOU
