OL,3,C'Some things I witnessed, no human
OL,4,Cshould have to live with'
OL,6,F"We walked past the car into SD Kells."
OL,8,FAsked if he thought often about the
OL,9,Ffact that his family had walked past
OL,10,Fthe car moments before it exploded, Mr
OL,11,FSkelton said "yes".
OL,13,FHe told the inquiry he had become "fed
OL,14,Fup" with shopping for shoes so left
OL,15,Fhis wife and daughter Shauna in SD
OL,16,FKells while he went into a separate
OL,17,Fshop.
OL,19,FHe said as he was about to leave this
OL,20,Fshop, the bomb exploded.
