OL,3,C'Some things I witnessed, no human
OL,4,Cshould have to live with'
OL,6,FMr Skelton said: "The front of the
OL,7,Fshop was sucked out and I walked out
OL,8,Fafter it."
OL,10,FHe added: "I walked out and went in
OL,11,Fthrough where the window was in SD
OL,12,FKells and I found her (Philomena)
OL,13,Flying face down in the rubble."
OL,15,FMr Skelton said he felt for his wife's
OL,16,Fpulse but could not find it.
OL,18,FHe told the inquiry he began to dig as
OL,19,Fhe believed his daughter Shauna was
OL,20,Fburied in the rubble.
