OL,3,C'Some things I witnessed, no human
OL,4,Cshould have to live with'
OL,6,FMr Skelton added: "I thought Shauna
OL,7,Fwas gone too. I didn't know about my
OL,8,Fother two daughters.
OL,10,F"My whole family, including myself,
OL,11,Fcould have been wiped out."
OL,13,FHe said the scenes of devastation in
OL,14,Fthe middle of the town were
OL,15,F"unbelievable".
OL,17,FMr Skelton said: "How so many people
OL,18,Fsurvived, it is a mystery to me."
