OL,6,FHe told the inquiry that he was
OL,7,Fushered out of SD Kells but kept going
OL,8,Fback to search for his daughter,
OL,9,Fstating "nobody could calm me down".
OL,11,FMr Skelton told the inquiry that a
OL,12,Fstranger then shouted over to him "you
OL,13,Fhave a wee ginger-haired girl?"
OL,15,FHe said: "I said I had. He said she
OL,16,Fwas in the hospital.
OL,18,F"That was the first time I knew Shauna
OL,19,Fwas alive."
